  "body": "The EVM `EXP` opcode (`0x0a`) arguments are two unsigned int.\nHence, solidity compiler should output an error (or at least a warning) for the following code:\n\n```\nint x = 5;\nint y = -3;\nint z = x ** y;\n```\n",
